        "style: Cinematic Realism v1, mood: cinematic, moody, controlled lighting, color palette: warm highlights, cool shadows. cinematic live-action video shot. scene: Apartment Kitchen Night. red fridge, wooden table, rainy window. lighting: dim warm lamp + blue moonlight. character (charA_v1): short_black, white_hoodie + black_jeans, silver_ring_left_hand. prop (mug_red_v1): state: story_clue, visually consistent. 桌上有一只红杯，杯沿还冒着热气。那不是他的杯子。, 林澈低声说：谁来过我家？. Narration: \"桌上有一只红杯，杯沿还冒着热气。那不是他的杯子。\". 林澈 says: \"谁来过我家？\". Camera motion: medium shot, subtle hand-held camera feel, focus on subject action. continuity locks: charA_v1 (location: apartment_kitchen_or_hallway, pose: searching); mug_red_v1 (location: near_main_character, state: warm_and_unexplained). cinematic realistic suspense comic panel, stable young Chinese man identity, rainy old apartment, red mug as recurring clue, coherent low-cost storyboard frame. Shot-to-shot continuity: maintain identical character identity, scene layout, lighting and prop positions as established in previous shot. Visual style must match preceding frame. Do not introduce new visual elements not present in the reference images. Character identity locked to reference images. No face morphing or outfit variation.. Scene layout locked to context reference frame. Do not reposition props or alter lighting source.. All props match reference images exactly. Prop must_keep: shape, color, size, material unchanged.. Camera transition smooth from previous shot continuity frame. No abrupt jump cut between shots. Stable visual consistency across entire clip. No character drift, no prop mutation, no scene layout shift."
